name: ACYA WFH DESIGN CHALLENGE 2020 (MEMORY TOKEN)
description: IN 2020, ACYA HAD ORGANIZE A PANDEMIC CONSCIOUS HOUSE DESIGN COMPETITION AS PART OF ITS PROGRAM TO MOTIVATE YOUNG ARCHITECTS DURING INITIAL PERIOD OF THE COVID 19 PANDEMIC. 700 PARTICIPANTS REGISTERED AND 100 SUBMITTED. THE COMPETITION WAS CONVENED BY AR DENNY SETIAWAN (INDONESIA) WITH THE ASSISTANCE OF YOGYAKARTA YOUNG ARCHITECTS UNDER THE LEADERSHIP OF ACYA CHAIRMAN AR RIDHA RAZAK(MALAYSIA & DEPUTY CHAIRMAN AR BISMA ASKARI (PAKISTAN)
